edBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T19:10:24.000Z","msg":"個個都好似無咗件事<br />\n佢身為香港特首 言而無信<br />\n點以身作則教育下一代？<br />\n點解冇記者問佢呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇佢點答<br />\n我估又係答 國不可一日無君 遲啲再算 之類嗰啲濕鳩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7wBtsLQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7wBtsLQ.png&h=0f481da0&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T00:30:07.000Z","msg":"因為主流好可圈好點<br />\n暫時我哋近期最多係有13萬人遊行<br />\n但係撐修例個邊已經拎到超過40萬個簽名<br />\n先唔理佢係咪做數 因為一定係<br />\n不過暫時反修例呢邊 都係唔知有幾多人<br />\n所以9/6遊行人數真係好緊要<br />\n如果聲音都係反修例，要佢落台<br />\n記者一定會問「林鄭點回應市民要求你落台嘅意見」<br />\n所以香港人要加油，一定要出來遊行，唔係就逼問唔到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa3266da8e7f5ed0dbb1627e032e1c30a14e2ce4","tid":1174333,"uid":253954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T00:39:28.000Z","msg":"你信佢尻up?<br />\n之前佢夠話自己唔會選特首啦，<br />\n後尾共狗欽點佢咪又衝出黎柒<br />\n大話精<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29b5e25ea73f7b5984d4339f35e26ee6020de7e7","tid":1174333,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T00:40:38.000Z","msg":"主流==&gt;主人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc6b3ce7d37504c64e99cca5c18bd0fd9ef9af45","tid":1174333,"uid":83523,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T00:48:43.000Z","msg":"佢個樣真係越來越西<br />\n<br />\n只睇佢幅相 你話佢無奶過共都無人信<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r93fT5R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr93fT5R.png&h=bb42c372&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49a0e9313ae85232111a3dd676d7371e44d43a08","tid":1174333,"uid":85284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T01:55:29.000Z","msg":"其實睇一個人咩料<br />\n聽佢講一兩次嘢，就已經知道一個大概<br />\n如果係可以長期聽到佢講嘢<br />\n一年半載就已經摸到至少七八成<br />\n個人醒唔醒目，基本上係同讀書叻唔叻無關<br />\n講嘢有冇內涵，到唔到位<br />\n說話可以反映目光／眼界銳唔銳利，多唔多廢話<br />\n會唔會為自己留有轉彎餘地，俾空間自己隨時能進能退<br />\n講嘢嘅佈局，甚至高手講嘢時<br />\n不經意地一路套料兼且 set 埋個氹俾對手踩<br />\n但係望下呢位阿太<br />\n意氣風發時完全冇諗過居安思危<br />\n講嘢不留餘地<br />\n往往最後都係會自己受番"},{"pid":"d9cd01078108b46e0be32c6fde50925b893e0f84","tid":1174333,"uid":117896,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T01:56:21.000Z","msg":"連登主流＝香港主流？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1b21d75c580ace4eeeb2ea8345800b4f94bf513","tid":1174333,"uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d9cd01078108b46e0be32c6fde50925b893e0f84","tid":1174333,"uid":117896,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T01:56:21.000Z","msg":"連登主流＝香港主流？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T01:56:53.000Z","msg":"市民對特首林鄭月娥的評分繼續維持不及格水平，只有49分；同時市民對目前香港的民生和政治狀況不滿率上升，不滿民生狀況的人增至近60%，不滿政治狀況的人更逼近65%。"},{"pid":"d62e0724e102a95483905719ab39ca4e2cdf0577","tid":1174333,"uid":5005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T01:58:46.000Z","msg":"佢眼中既主流意見都支持佢喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n28國都只係宣示姐 都無任何反對意見<br />\n100萬人上街都仲有600萬人支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊會輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c5a3af9848fc19bc0bcc8b30062fdccfaf25789","tid":1174333,"uid":143078,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T02:01:25.000Z","msg":"只係少數被誤導，無知市民嘅聲音<br />\n<br />\n香港絕大部市民仍然支持特區政府，中央政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8f1888d38e2f99211c124c2f2091907f5aba465","tid":1174333,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T03:01:30.000Z","msg":"柒婆：有咩？我聽唔到喎"},{"pid":"80bd28432b69